description: Best practices for Spatie Media Library usage

Use the addMediaFromRequest method for efficient and secure media handling from user uploads.
Define Media Collections to organize media and apply specific conversions and properties.
Optimize images by defining conversions to create different sizes for various use cases.
Implement proper validation for media uploads using Laravel's built-in validation rules.
Use withResponsiveImages() to automatically generate srcset attributes for responsive images in your views.

